sebelum sholat jumatThis course is made by the University of Pennsylvania and lasts about five weeks. This course is designed to improve the quality of their English in terms of business and entrepreneurship. Each week you will learn many things. This course provides material in the form of explanatory videos, readings, and quizzes. The material presented while I was following this course was quite easy to understand because of the subtitles on the video explanation of the material and also the practice questions included in the video. In addition, this course is also interesting for me because the material presented includes knowledge which for me is about business and entrepreneurship. Therefore, I think this course is one of the recommended courses to improve English vocabulary in business and entrepreneurship and provide additional knowledge related to business and entrepreneurship.

I love the ease of navigating through the Coursera.  The weekly modules presented in written and video formats were not heavy and time-consuming.  I have a full-time job, so my time for Coursera begins at 10:00 pm.  The videos were consistently short, not exceeding 6 minutes in duration, by what I've seen.  Also, the video presentations were simple, spot-on, employed minimal graphics, just to get the point across.  I also loved the words/terminologies featured in the slides, which makes the participant/student enrich his/her own business vocabulary and retain much information.  Thank you, Dr. Nichols and Dr. Redeli for the learnings in this program.  God bless.
